<bio>
<p>Cathy is the demonstration nurse for Mesa Public Schools in Mesa, Arizona, and an instructor in nursing continuing education at Gateway Community College. She has been a school nurse for 19 years, most of which in special education. Prior to school nursing, she worked in emergency and pre-hospital care. Cathy is also the owner of Hands On Learning, a company that manufactures The Nickie<sup>®</sup> Medical Training Doll.</p>
